Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter on energy policy
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407cht
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 15 May 1977
President Carter issues warning on the US's over-consumption of energy and what this means for future generations. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less